The spatial magic user will stand by here.

00:18:15.500 --> 00:18:18.030
Roger-dodger-roger!

00:18:18.620 --> 00:18:20.780
You'd better put your all into this.

00:18:21.140 --> 00:18:22.210
Let's go!

00:18:32.470 --> 00:18:37.760
Do you know why you're in this mess?

00:18:38.700 --> 00:18:43.860
It's because you're a citizen 
of the Clover Kingdom.

00:18:45.100 --> 00:18:49.190
I was a citizen there myself, 
until not so long ago.

00:18:49.190 --> 00:18:50.310
But...

00:18:51.010 --> 00:18:53.310
I was different.

00:18:55.990 --> 00:19:00.160
Lord Licht gave me my true name.

00:19:04.130 --> 00:19:08.870
We're special, you see.

00:19:10.970 --> 00:19:17.990
So we can do whatever we 
want to trash like you.

00:19:27.580 --> 00:19:29.410
He's way too weak.

00:19:29.410 --> 00:19:31.740
There are stronger guys, right?

00:19:31.740 --> 00:19:35.820
Do leave me some chances 
to strike beautifully.

00:19:36.250 --> 00:19:37.800
Are you all right?

00:19:37.800 --> 00:19:39.410
Thank you so much.

00:19:41.730 --> 00:19:45.020
I'm sure you don't need detailed plans.

00:19:45.710 --> 00:19:48.870
Take down any enemies you encounter 
as you proceed toward the center.

00:19:49.500 --> 00:19:50.620
You may do that

00:19:50.620 --> 00:19:53.020
however you prefer!

00:19:55.940 --> 00:19:59.130
I don't care what you do 
as long as you don't lose.

00:20:02.100 --> 00:20:04.540
Ah, the ants show themselves at last.

00:20:07.420 --> 00:20:14.150
I hear you caused quite a mess at 
the royal capital while I was away.

00:20:15.860 --> 00:20:20.900
You will not escape like you 
did from a certain cave.

00:20:21.290 --> 00:20:24.390
Eye of the Midnight Sun, we've come...

00:20:24.390 --> 00:20:25.620
...to get our revenge.

00:20:25.620 --> 00:20:29.660
How dare you do that to my rival...

00:20:29.660 --> 00:20:31.700
To my foolish little brother...

00:20:32.370 --> 00:20:34.540
You shall pay dearly!

00:20:35.030 --> 00:20:37.960
I will be the one to take your leader's head!

00:20:40.460 --> 00:20:42.890
H-Holy crap!

00:20:42.890 --> 00:20:44.970
Wait, do we even need to be here?!

00:20:51.020 --> 00:20:54.550
Looks like someone dangerous showed up.

00:20:54.550 --> 00:20:56.980
Licht is gone right now, too.

00:21:01.050 --> 00:21:04.410
Guess I shouldn't be so lazy 
about this and just go.

00:22:36.000 --> 00:22:40.500
Petit Clover

00:22:36.660 --> 00:22:39.430
Petit Clover!

00:22:40.000 --> 00:22:44.000
Lazy Raia!

00:22:41.060 --> 00:22:42.870
Lazy Raia!

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:46.190
Lord Raia! Lord Raia!

00:22:47.970 --> 00:22:50.010
What's up? Why are you so panicked?

00:22:50.010 --> 00:22:51.210
We're being attacked!

00:22:51.210 --> 00:22:53.190
Sounds like it.

00:22:53.190 --> 00:22:56.660
But it's such a pain to deal with them.

00:22:56.660 --> 00:22:58.490
What?! Please don't be like that!

00:22:58.490 --> 00:23:00.020
It's a pain to get up.

00:23:00.370 --> 00:23:01.690
I shall sit you up.

00:23:01.690 --> 00:23:04.190
It's a pain to put shoes on.

00:23:04.190 --> 00:23:05.710
I shall do that, too!

00:23:06.350 --> 00:23:08.360
It's a pain to stand up.

00:23:08.360 --> 00:23:09.530
Up you go.

00:23:10.380 --> 00:23:14.180
Walking is a huge pain! 
Yeah, I'm not gonna do it.

00:23:14.180 --> 00:23:15.120
What?!

00:23:15.120 --> 00:23:16.940
Please reconsider!

00:23:18.830 --> 00:23:22.650
I think I was sleeping with my mouth open,
 because my throat hurts...

00:23:22.650 --> 00:23:24.130
I'll give you this lollipop!

00:23:24.450 --> 00:23:25.880
What flavor is it?

00:23:25.880 --> 00:23:27.880
A-Apple...

00:23:30.420 --> 00:23:33.390
I guess I shouldn't be so 
lazy about this and just go.

00:23:34.580 --> 00:23:37.260
What would've happened if 
it was an orange lollipop?

00:23:39.700 --> 00:23:43.820
Come to think of it, I wonder how 
Valtos and the others are doing.

